T:Autodesk.Revit.UI.Mechanical.IDuctFitt.title: IDuctFittingAndAccessoryPressureDropUIServer Interface
T:Autodesk.Revit.UI.Mechanical.IDuctFitt.desc: Interface for external servers providing optional UI for duct fitting and duct accessory coefficient calculation.
T:Autodesk.Revit.UI.Mechanical.IDuctFitt.remarks: This service works with duct fitting and accessory pressure drop service. It provides the settings for the duct fitting and accessory pressure drop server if needed; and it also provides UI for user to input the settings in Revit. A typical way to use the external server can be: Implement a server class that derives from this interface Create a new server object and register it with the service.
